# Next.js app is a separate Vercel project (onetradingsocial-app).
# Shipping it into the static/marketing deploy makes /app resolve to a real
# directory on the filesystem, which the trailingSlash:false normalizer
# 308-loops onto itself before the /app/* rewrite can proxy it.
app/
